ono,

00:41:38.344 --> 00:41:40.804
ovima je upravo pao dron od 50 milja
dolara

00:41:42.224 --> 00:41:47.264
i dron nakon par sekundi padne između nas,
znači u prostor nekih pet

00:41:48.224 --> 00:41:48.644
metara.

00:41:49.344 --> 00:41:49.864
I dron

00:41:51.384 --> 00:41:53.564
punom težinom s baterijom zvizne o pod

00:41:54.184 --> 00:41:56.744
i prebaci se kao kornjača naopačke.

00:41:57.784 --> 00:41:58.084
I

00:41:59.124 --> 00:42:01.624
mi gledamo, ah, fuck, one more down.

00:42:02.844 --> 00:42:09.684
I ni pet ni šest, kolega bzbzbzbz vrati ga
